Dialogue: 10,0:00:23.39,0:00:27.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nanoka, apa kau baru saja memakai pedangku?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:30.61,0:00:33.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tadi aku hanya mau memotong jaringnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:33.82,0:00:36.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pedang itu cuma bisa dipakai olehku.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:36.53,0:00:37.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hah?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:40.74,0:00:42.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pedang ini, sama sepertiku,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.29,0:00:44.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,terkena kutukan Byoki.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:45.37,0:00:47.00,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Kutukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:47.08,0:00:48.00,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Apa maksudnya?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:48.92,0:00:49.80,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Ini…
Dialogue: 10,0:00:49.96,0:00:51.80,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Pedang Hagunsei.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:51.88,0:00:52.76,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Dulu sekali,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:52.84,0:00:55.88,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,pedang ini kupakai saat melawan Byoki.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:56.64,0:00:57.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di tengah pertarungan,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:57.80,0:00:59.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,pedang ini bermandikan darah Byoki
Dialogue: 10,0:01:00.31,0:01:01.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan berubah menjadi pedang terkutuk.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:03.35,0:01:05.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bermandikan darah dan terkutuk?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:06.44,0:01:07.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah berkali-kali
Dialogue: 10,0:01:07.48,0:01:10.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,bandit atau yokai mencoba\Nmencuri pedang ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:11.61,0:01:12.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bandit?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:13.24,0:01:15.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa pun yang memakai Pedang Hagunsei,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:15.78,0:01:16.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,tanpa terkecuali,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:16.86,0:01:19.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,pada akhirnya akan muntah darah\Ndan mati mengenaskan.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:23.58,0:01:25.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tiap kali mereka mencoba\Nmengayunkan pedang ini,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:25.79,0:01:27.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,darah beracun Byoki\Nakan menggerogoti tubuh mereka.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:29.08,0:01:30.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pedang ini juga
Dialogue: 10,0:01:31.67,0:01:33.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,selalu kembali kepadaku,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:34.26,0:01:36.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,tak peduli berapa kali dicuri\Nataupun kubuang.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:36.68,0:01:38.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar-benar mirip kutukan.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:39.05,0:01:40.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berarti…
Dialogue: 10,0:01:41.43,0:01:44.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena aku baik-baik saja setelah memakai
Dialogue: 10,0:01:45.23,0:01:46.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pedang Hagunsei…
Dialogue: 10,0:01:47.27,0:01:48.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nanoka.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:48.73,0:01:51.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan-jangan, kau juga dikutuk oleh Byoki.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:53.57,0:01:54.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anu…
Dialogue: 10,0:01:55.40,0:01:57.78,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Aku tahu kalian masih mau
Dialogue: 10,0:01:59.11,0:02:00.91,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,membahas hal penting, tapi…
Dialogue: 10,0:02:01.74,0:02:02.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Hah?\N- Apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.84,0:03:43.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Otoya! Kau kenapa?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.89,0:03:45.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini terjadi
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.01,0:03:47.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,saat kalian sedang bertarung.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.93,0:03:49.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku terkena imbasnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.73,0:03:51.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berarti…
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.94,0:03:53.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,ini salahku?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.90,0:03:55.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maafkan aku, Otoya.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.79,0:03:58.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku takkan membiarkan Nanoka\Nmemegang pedang ini lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.30,0:04:00.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tolong pastikan\Ndia tak pernah melakukannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.82,0:04:03.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku yang
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.16,0:04:05.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,menyebabkan ini padamu?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.24,0:04:11.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sayoko. Kau sudah sadar?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.96,0:04:13.79,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Dokter Mao.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.63,0:04:15.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang baru saja terjadi?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.96,0:04:19.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sayoko,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.55,0:04:23.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,tolong hubungi polisi setelah kami pergi.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.38,0:04:26.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mereka pasti akan menanyaimu,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.68,0:04:29.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi bilang saja kau pingsan\Ndan tidak tahu apa-apa.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.60,0:04:30.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi…
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.89,0:04:31.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tenang saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.89,0:04:34.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mereka akan segera sadar
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.77,0:04:36.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,kalau pelakunya bukan manusia.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.52,0:04:38.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo pergi, Nanoka.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.24,0:04:42.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia pingsan lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.53,0:04:45.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bangun.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.70,0:04:54.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hii…
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.25,0:04:56.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa aku membunuhnya?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.92,0:04:58.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku yang membunuhnya, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.75,0:05:00.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tidak apa-apa, Otoya?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.42,0:05:01.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Otoya?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.67,0:05:02.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tubuhmu terbelah dua!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.13,0:05:05.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Astaga.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.55,0:05:07.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Boneka aslinya juga ikut retak.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.35,0:05:15.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini, Otoya.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.24,0:05:25.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hah?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.53,0:05:32.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kerusakannya sudah dipindahkan ke jimat ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.92,0:05:40.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Retaknya hilang.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.17,0:05:43.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah diperbaiki.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.80,0:05:44.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagus.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.17,0:05:46.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Omong-omong…
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.43,0:05:49.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Otoya, kau ini sebenarnya apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.93,0:05:51.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ini shikigami.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.47,0:05:53.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Shikigami?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.10,0:05:55.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tidak mendengarkan, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.02,0:05:58.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tuan Mao menyalurkan\Nkekuatan spiritualnya ke boneka ini
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.85,0:06:00.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,agar aku bisa hidup.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.61,0:06:01.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berarti…
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.77,0:06:04.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Wujud aslimu itu…
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.03,0:06:05.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.99,0:06:06.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.99,0:06:09.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku benar-benar tidak paham.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.12,0:06:11.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi syukurlah kau selamat.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.87,0:06:14.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Padahal aku tadi hampir mati, tahu.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.33,0:06:15.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hah?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.58,0:06:17.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang lebih penting,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.92,0:06:19.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,mari bahas masalahmu, Nanoka.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.38,0:06:22.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau kau memang dikutuk Byoki,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.30,0:06:25.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,berarti kau pernah bertemu dengannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.47,0:06:29.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siluman yang kau lihat waktu kecil itu…
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.68,0:06:31.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maksudmu
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.80,0:06:33.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,itu Byoki?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.85,0:06:38.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Seingatku, setelah kejadian itu,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.48,0:06:40.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,mereka menemukanku berlumuran darah.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.69,0:06:44.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selama ini kukira\Nitu darahku sendiri, tapi…
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.98,0:06:47.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan-jangan itu darah Byoki?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.36,0:06:49.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tidak ingat?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.07,0:06:50.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak…
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.37,0:06:52.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aneh, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.12,0:06:53.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.08,0:06:55.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi waktu itu ada kebakaran!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.29,0:06:58.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kotanya terbakar…
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.62,0:07:02.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tuan Mao, dugaan kita benar
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.92,0:07:04.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,kalau kota ini terhubung dengan Byoki.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.55,0:07:07.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Byoki yang Nanoka temui saat kecil itu…
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.76,0:07:08.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di mana kejadiannya?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.18,0:07:11.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Penghalang ini…
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.05,0:07:14.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Penghalang\Nyang cuma bisa dilewati oleh Nanoka.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.72,0:07:17.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mau pulang untuk cari tahu.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.02,0:07:18.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nanoka.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.02,0:07:21.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bawa ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.15,0:07:25.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.69,0:07:26.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini obat penawar.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.07,0:07:29.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Minumlah saat kekuatanmu hilang\Ndan kau sedang dalam bahaya.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.32,0:07:31.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.11,0:07:34.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di duniaku, justru lebih bahaya
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.49,0:07:36.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,kalau kekuatanku tiba-tiba muncul.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.96,0:07:43.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah malam?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.33,0:07:47.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Padahal masih pagi\Nsaat aku pergi dari dunia sana.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.84,0:07:49.72,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Nanoka!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.42,0:07:52.63,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Dari mana saja kau seminggu ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.01,0:07:54.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Seminggu?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.68,0:07:56.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Padahal aku cuma semalam di sana.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.47,0:07:59.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku benar-benar tak paham konsep waktunya.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.23,0:08:01.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nona Nanoka.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.90,0:08:04.77,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Kakekmu sangat khawatir
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.19,0:08:06.90,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,sampai beliau jatuh pingsan.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.15,0:08:07.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hah?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.44,0:08:10.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maafkan aku, Kakek!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.74,0:08:15.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Untungnya Kakek tidak memarahiku.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.87,0:08:19.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selamat pagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.04,0:08:22.75,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Kau bersikap\Nseolah tak terjadi apa-apa, Nanoka!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.12,0:08:24.67,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Kudengar kau masuk rumah sakit?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.92,0:08:26.84,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Fisikmu benar-benar lemah, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.21,0:08:28.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau sudah tidak apa-apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.59,0:08:31.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya… Aku sudah baikan sekarang.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.59,0:08:33.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Syukurlah!\N- Kami semua sangat khawatir.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.26,0:08:34.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Terima kasih.\N- Jangan memaksakan diri, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.59,0:08:36.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Uozumi pasti beralasan begitu\Nkepada pihak sekolah.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.18,0:08:38.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih, Uozumi.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.35,0:08:40.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi yang lebih penting,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.97,0:08:42.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku harus menyelidiki kecelakaan itu!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.60,0:08:48.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Sekitar siang hari pada 1 September 2011,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.23,0:08:51.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,terjadi insiden jalan ambles\Ndi Jalan Kelima."
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.69,0:08:54.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Satu keluarga beranggotakan tiga orang\Nterperosok ke dalamnya,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.36,0:08:57.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,menewaskan sepasang suami istri."
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.70,0:09:00.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Putri mereka yang berusia tujuh tahun\Nterlempar ke luar mobil,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.45,0:09:02.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan selamat secara ajaib…"
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.75,0:09:06.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini sama sekali tidak membantu.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.71,0:09:09.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sudah tahu semua informasi itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.84,0:09:11.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau sedang lihat apa, Nanoka?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.42,0:09:13.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cuma cari-cari info sedikit.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.13,0:09:15.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tumben sekali…
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.51,0:09:16.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,kau melakukan riset.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.18,0:09:19.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi aku tidak jago soal beginian.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.60,0:09:21.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya aku tidak pernah\Nmenemukan jawaban yang kucari.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.31,0:09:24.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu…
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.52,0:09:25.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Cocok, 'kan?\N- Cocok, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.77,0:09:27.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Hei, Shiraha!\N- Hei, Shiraha!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.27,0:09:30.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Bisa minta waktunya sebentar?\N- Bisa minta waktunya sebentar?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.94,0:09:32.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian ini kenapa?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.65,0:09:33.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nanoka bilang…
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.86,0:09:35.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,dia butuh bantuanmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.61,0:09:36.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Untuk riset sesuatu.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.11,0:09:38.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Boleh. Mau cari apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.95,0:09:39.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.37,0:09:42.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,soal insiden jalan ambles di Jalan Kelima.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.54,0:09:43.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hah?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.66,0:09:44.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.37,0:09:47.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menurutku kecelakaan itu juga janggal.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.42,0:09:54.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Janggal? Apanya?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.88,0:09:56.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pertama,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.26,0:09:59.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,mereka tidak pernah menemukan
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.22,0:10:01.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,penyebab jalan ambles itu, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.89,0:10:04.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu bukan ambles biasa.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.73,0:10:05.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sini, lihat.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.27,0:10:07.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagian ini
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.35,0:10:09.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,seolah-olah hancur terkeruk
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.81,0:10:11.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,oleh kekuatan besar dari arah samping.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.48,0:10:12.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dari samping?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.65,0:10:16.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan-jangan itu berasal\Ndari arah jalan perbelanjaan yang sepi itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.82,0:10:18.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau dipikir-pikir…
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.91,0:10:22.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sisi sebelah sana
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.53,0:10:23.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,hangus terbakar.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.83,0:10:26.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pasti ada sesuatu yang terjadi.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.54,0:10:30.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi apa, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.96,0:10:33.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa ada hal lain yang kau temukan, Shiraha?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.88,0:10:35.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hah? Anu…
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.51,0:10:37.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.43,0:10:41.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini unggahan dari pejalan kaki\Ndi hari kejadian.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.51,0:10:43.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tulisannya,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.89,0:10:45.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Waktu mereka mencoba\Nmenyelamatkan anak perempuan itu,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.27,0:10:48.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,sarung tangan tim penyelamat meleleh.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.14,0:10:50.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa itu cairan asam?"
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.48,0:10:54.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sarung tangan mereka\Nmeleleh karena menyentuh
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.32,0:10:55.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,darah di tubuhku?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.53,0:10:58.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan-jangan itu racun dari darah Byoki?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.86,0:10:59.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga menemukan…
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.91,0:11:03.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,beberapa artikel lanjutan\Ndari majalah mingguan.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:03.95,0:11:05.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi artikelnya…
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.45,0:11:06.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Isinya apa? Beri tahu aku!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.08,0:11:08.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yaitu…
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.62,0:11:10.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Contohnya yang ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.25,0:11:12.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Seorang anak berusia tujuh tahun\Nberhasil diselamatkan."
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.59,0:11:17.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Namun, semua kaca mobil\Nyang ringsek itu masih tertutup rapat.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.46,0:11:20.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, bagaimana anak itu bisa berada\Ndi luar mobil masih menjadi misteri."
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.26,0:11:22.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kira-kira seperti itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.26,0:11:25.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar juga. Saat kejadian,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.39,0:11:29.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,seingatku aku merasa seperti ditarik
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.43,0:11:30.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,oleh kekuatan yang sangat besar.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.77,0:11:36.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa aku tak bisa mengingat\Nkejadian waktu itu, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.19,0:11:39.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih, Shiraha.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.53,0:11:43.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Andai saja aku bisa lebih berguna.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.74,0:11:44.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi aku jadi penasaran.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.74,0:11:47.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa kau menyelidiki kecelakaan itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.25,0:11:49.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Soalnya…
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.71,0:11:52.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anak yang diselamatkan itu…
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.83,0:11:54.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,kau, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.71,0:11:55.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anu…
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.17,0:11:58.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf kalau ini terdengar aneh.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.76,0:12:01.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukannya aku mau ikut campur\Natau sekadar iseng.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.84,0:12:05.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hanya saja aku tidak bisa\Nberhenti memikirkannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.64,0:12:07.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Memikirkan apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.02,0:12:10.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yah, habisnya…
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.89,0:12:12.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau itu sangat kuat, Nanoka.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.15,0:12:14.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kuat?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.61,0:12:15.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.44,0:12:18.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mana mungkin.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.28,0:12:21.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fisikku lemah dan aku payah berolahraga.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.70,0:12:22.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maksudku…
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.28,0:12:25.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau sudah melalui banyak hal\Nseperti kecelakaan itu dan lainnya,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.37,0:12:28.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi kau tidak pernah menunjukkannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.33,0:12:29.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau selalu ceria.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.91,0:12:31.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mentalmu sangat kuat.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.75,0:12:34.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia memujiku… sepertinya…
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.12,0:12:37.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau itu… Menurutku kau sangat…
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.25,0:12:38.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Shiraha!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.05,0:12:39.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.51,0:12:42.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh, tidak perlu berterima kasih!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.05,0:12:45.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sampai jumpa di sekolah!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.89,0:12:48.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dah!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.64,0:12:49.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Aduh!\N- Maaf!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.02,0:12:51.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, Nanoka…
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.43,0:12:52.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana hasilnya kemarin
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.89,0:12:53.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,dengan Shiraha?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.35,0:12:56.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia tahu jauh lebih banyak daripada aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.23,0:12:59.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah kuduga.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.82,0:13:01.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia sampai terus-terusan merisetnya, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.11,0:13:04.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Memangnya kenapa?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.36,0:13:05.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau masih belum paham juga?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.24,0:13:10.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Shiraha itu bukannya peduli\Ndengan kecelakaannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.99,0:13:12.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia itu menyukaimu.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.21,0:13:14.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hah?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.25,0:13:19.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tuh, 'kan? Dia baru saja menatapmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.42,0:13:21.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia selalu memperhatikanmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.92,0:13:23.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kelihatan jelas sekali, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.17,0:13:26.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, jadi begitu alasannya?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.01,0:13:33.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Permisi, Dokter Mao ada di mana, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.77,0:13:35.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lewat sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.73,0:13:37.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pasien berikutnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.11,0:13:41.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa ini ramai-ramai?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.61,0:13:45.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selamat datang kembali, Nona Nanoka.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.78,0:13:47.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami menemukan bangunan kosong,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.57,0:13:48.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,jadi kami buka klinik di sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.20,0:13:50.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Buka klinik?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.03,0:13:52.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aduh…
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.24,0:13:53.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau cacingan.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.71,0:13:56.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akan kuberikan obat untuk membasminya.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.79,0:13:58.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.04,0:13:59.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berikutnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.34,0:14:01.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:01.30,0:14:03.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ternyata dia tidak berniat\Nmembasmi semua yokai.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.30,0:14:06.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada yokai yang cinta damai,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.09,0:14:09.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,ada juga yang ganas dan\Nsuka memangsa manusia.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.76,0:14:11.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sama saja seperti manusia.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.31,0:14:13.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lagi pula,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.52,0:14:15.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,sepertinya Tuan Mao memang selalu
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.27,0:14:18.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,lebih jago menyembuhkan\Ndaripada menghancurkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.65,0:14:20.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Masa iya?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.65,0:14:23.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lebih jago menyembuhkan\Ndaripada menghancurkan?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.57,0:14:25.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, Nanoka…
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.28,0:14:28.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dari mana saja kau sepuluh hari ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.45,0:14:29.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepuluh hari?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.66,0:14:32.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Padahal aku cuma pulang selama dua hari.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.66,0:14:36.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selama kau pergi,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.58,0:14:38.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,kami mengumpulkan informasi.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.63,0:14:42.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebagian besar pasien kami adalah yokai\Ndari sekitar sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.38,0:14:45.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, kau mengorek info\Nsambil mengobati mereka?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.63,0:14:48.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nanoka, katamu\Nkau pernah ke sini saat masih kecil
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.18,0:14:51.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan melihat kota ini kebakaran, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.05,0:14:52.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Iya.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.39,0:14:56.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ternyata tidak ada satu pun\Nyang pernah dengar soal kebakaran itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.52,0:14:57.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hah?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.23,0:14:59.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak mungkin!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.77,0:15:01.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mana mungkin tidak pernah ada kebakaran?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.40,0:15:08.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi kota itu\Ndan jalan perbelanjaan yang sepi itu
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.15,0:15:09.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,jelas-jelas saling terhubung.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.74,0:15:13.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebenarnya apa yang terjadi?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.55,0:15:31.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pendeta Shoko!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.84,0:15:33.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pendeta Shoko! Tolong berkati kami!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.89,0:15:36.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di mana kau, Yoriko?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.18,0:15:38.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia itu penipu!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.60,0:15:41.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yoriko! Ayo kita pulang!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.27,0:15:42.56,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,- Tidak mau!\N- Hentikan!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.69,0:15:43.61,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Ayo pulang, Yoriko!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.69,0:15:44.82,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Jangan begini, Ayah!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.98,0:15:46.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau bisa kena azab nanti!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.57,0:15:47.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Omong kosong!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.82,0:15:51.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau wanita itu benar-benar orang sakti
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.45,0:15:53.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,yang bisa mengatur umur manusia sesukanya,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.37,0:15:55.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,coba saja suruh dia membunuhku\Ndengan kesaktiannya!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.20,0:15:59.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tiga hari.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.25,0:16:04.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Umurmu hanya tersisa tiga hari lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.21,0:16:07.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar saja, tiga hari kemudian…
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.80,0:16:11.22,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,pria itu sungguhan…
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.30,0:16:12.89,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,meninggal.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.64,0:16:15.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa penyebab kematiannya?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.47,0:16:17.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Serangan jantung…
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.97,0:16:19.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kurasa begitu sebutannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.02,0:16:22.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Padahal dia terlihat sehat-sehat saja\Nsehari sebelumnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.48,0:16:24.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Makanya,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.52,0:16:26.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,seluruh kota geger dengan rumor
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.69,0:16:29.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,kalau Pendeta Shoko\Nmengutuknya sampai mati.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.03,0:16:32.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mengutuk?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.41,0:16:35.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Haruskah kita selidiki, Tuan Mao?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.03,0:16:38.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau harus ke sana, soalnya…
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.62,0:16:40.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,katanya Pendeta Shoko bisa mengatur
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.50,0:16:42.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,umur manusia.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.42,0:16:47.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mungkin saja wanita itu\Npernah bertemu Byoki.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.92,0:16:49.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hah? Maksudnya?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.63,0:16:52.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Byoki itu tahu cara…
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.51,0:16:53.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.09,0:16:56.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,memanipulasi umur manusia.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.47,0:16:58.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tuan!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.18,0:17:02.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa yang melakukan ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.49,0:17:13.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kucing?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.95,0:17:15.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ruang Pusaka menyimpan
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.49,0:17:17.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,gulungan rahasia\Nyang diwariskan turun-temurun.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.08,0:17:21.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tempat itu hanya boleh dimasuki
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.08,0:17:24.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,oleh guruku dan pewarisnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.67,0:17:27.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Byoki itu menyusup masuk
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.54,0:17:28.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan melahap gulungan rahasianya.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.75,0:17:30.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gulungan rahasia?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.38,0:17:34.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gulungan yang berisi mantra\Npengubah umur manusia?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.84,0:17:37.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu adalah jurus rahasia\Nterhebat dalam Onmyodo.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.34,0:17:38.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar begitu, Tuan Mao?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.55,0:17:39.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.06,0:17:43.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Byoki mendapatkan kekuatan itu\Nsetelah menelan gulungannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.73,0:17:44.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sulit dipercaya.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.19,0:17:48.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maksudmu dia men-download\Nisi gulungan itu dengan cara memakannya?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.27,0:17:49.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Down…
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.65,0:17:52.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nona Nanoka bicara apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.69,0:17:54.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Entahlah.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:54.78,0:17:55.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mau tanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.36,0:17:59.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu kejadiannya berapa tahun yang lalu?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.49,0:18:01.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berarti… Biar kuingat-ingat…
Dialogue: 10,0:18:02.04,0:18:03.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah cukup lama.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.54,0:18:05.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bicara soal "cukup lama"…
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.66,0:18:07.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebenarnya sudah lama aku penasaran.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.71,0:18:10.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Umurmu berapa?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.84,0:18:14.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sudah berhenti menghitungnya, jadi…
Dialogue: 10,0:18:15.38,0:18:16.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi…
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.72,0:18:18.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau dihitung sejak hari itu…
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.51,0:18:20.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mungkin sudah sekitar 900 tahun.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.93,0:18:22.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,900 tahun?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.02,0:18:26.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi intinya kau itu abadi?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.10,0:18:27.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.27,0:18:31.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Waktu itu Byoki gagal membunuhku,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.02,0:18:34.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,jadi dia hanya mengutuk tubuhku lalu kabur.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.40,0:18:38.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak begitu paham, tapi…
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.20,0:18:43.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berarti umurku juga ikut terpengaruh?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.95,0:18:44.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena itulah
Dialogue: 10,0:18:45.70,0:18:47.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,kita harus menemukan Byoki itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.08,0:18:49.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita harus menemukannya
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.83,0:18:51.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,agar kutukannya bisa dicabut.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.54,0:18:55.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pemimpin sekte wanita yang bisa\Nmengatur umur sesuka hati…
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.76,0:18:59.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan-jangan Pendeta Shoko\Nmempelajari ilmu itu
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.38,0:19:00.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,dari Byoki.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.14,0:19:02.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu maksudmu?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.14,0:19:05.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kecuali kalau dia cuma dukun palsu.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.02,0:19:09.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Makanya…
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.85,0:19:11.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau harus pergi ke sana, Nanoka.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.48,0:19:12.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hah?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.94,0:19:13.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.20,0:19:22.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, aku harus menyusup sendirian?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.83,0:19:26.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sekte Shorinkyo pimpinan Pendeta Shoko
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.45,0:19:28.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,menyebarkan ramalan kiamat.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.08,0:19:30.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu kisah yang umum.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.17,0:19:33.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia berjanji\Nbarang siapa yang setia mengikutinya,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.88,0:19:36.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,akan selamat dari hari kiamat.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.71,0:19:40.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pengikutnya didominasi\Noleh orang kaya atau siswi sekolah
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.30,0:19:43.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,yang masih muda dan polos.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.14,0:19:47.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nanoka, kau sangat cocok memerankan\Nsiswi sekolah yang polos itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.89,0:19:50.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Orang dengan tampang mencurigakan sepertiku
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.89,0:19:52.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,pasti dilarang masuk.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.86,0:19:55.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada benarnya juga, tapi…
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.40,0:19:58.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku merasa tak yakin tentang ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.19,0:20:02.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anggota baru boleh duduk di depan.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.49,0:20:05.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Boleh ya duduk di kursi sebagus itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.99,0:20:08.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tentu saja, silakan nikmati pengalaman\Nyang luar biasa ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.29,0:20:13.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rupanya itu Pendeta Shoko.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:14.50,0:20:16.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bintang Kehancuran,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.50,0:20:17.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bintang Lima Bumi Kuning,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.80,0:20:19.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,telah mencapai pusat langit.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.47,0:20:21.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku bisa melihatnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.97,0:20:24.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Api berkobar hebat,\Norang-orang berteriak panik…
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.01,0:20:27.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Serta tumpukan mayat di mana-mana.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.89,0:20:29.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Aku tidak mau mati!\N- Pendeta Shoko!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.81,0:20:31.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Apa yang harus kami perbuat?\N- Tolong beri tahu kami!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.06,0:20:33.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Selamatkan kami!\N- Pendeta Shoko!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.40,0:20:34.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bikin merinding saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.61,0:20:39.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hadirin sekalian, jangan putus asa.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.36,0:20:41.74,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Seperti yang kalian semua tahu,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.82,0:20:42.95,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Pendeta Shoko memiliki anugerah
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.03,0:20:46.62,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,untuk mengendalikan umur manusia.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.53,0:20:49.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di depan kalian ada batu pelindung
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.83,0:20:51.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,yang sudah diberkati oleh Pendeta Shoko.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.37,0:20:53.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Batu ini akan melindungi kalian
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.87,0:20:55.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,- dari marabahaya…\N- Hah? Malah jualan?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.88,0:20:58.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,- dan menyelamatkan kalian dari hari kiamat.\N- Tolong, beri saya satu!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.50,0:21:00.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kumohon, Pendeta Shoko!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.09,0:21:03.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anak saya menderita penyakit\Nyang tidak bisa disembuhkan!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.97,0:21:05.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bawa dia kemari.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.85,0:21:09.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kumohon, tolong sembuhkan dia!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.02,0:21:15.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tubuhnya bercahaya!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.99,0:21:29.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia membuka matanya!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.87,0:21:32.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benang kehidupannya\Ntelah tersambung kembali.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.50,0:21:34.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Luar biasa!\N- Pendeta Shoko berhasil lagi!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.67,0:21:36.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Pendeta Shoko!\N- Ini mukjizat!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.08,0:21:37.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Beliau menyelamatkan bayinya!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.09,0:21:39.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.71,0:21:40.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ibu!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.22,0:21:45.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kelihatannya terlalu dibuat-buat.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.89,0:21:51.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa dia gemetaran?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:52.43,0:21:54.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maksudmu dojo kumuh ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.48,0:21:57.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dulu hanya ada ayah dan putrinya\Nyang tinggal di sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:58.06,0:22:00.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Putrinya yang bernama Yoriko,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:00.94,0:22:03.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,dicuci otaknya oleh sebuah sekte baru.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:03.82,0:22:06.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Seingatku, ketua perguruan ini\Nmeninggal secara mendadak.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:07.03,0:22:07.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:08.24,0:22:10.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia meninggal tepat tiga hari
Dialogue: 10,0:22:10.53,0:22:11.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,setelah mencoba menjemput paksa putrinya.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:14.66,0:22:17.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menurut desas-desus, pendeta\Nsekte itu yang menyantetnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:17.92,0:22:18.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bikin ngeri saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:21.09,0:22:22.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ketemu, Tuan Mao!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:23.71,0:22:25.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini boneka kutukan.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:26.30,0:22:28.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Boneka ini dikubur di dekat pintu masuk\Nuntuk mengirim teluh.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:29.09,0:22:32.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya mereka memang paham\Nsoal ilmu hitam.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:33.39,0:22:34.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Beri saya batu pelindungnya!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:34.81,0:22:35.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saya juga mau!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:35.73,0:22:36.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Saya juga!\N- Buat saya satu!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:36.77,0:22:37.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tolong jangan dorong-dorongan!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:37.77,0:22:39.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Silakan letakkan sumbangan Anda di sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:39.15,0:22:41.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Harap antre.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:41.23,0:22:42.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saya beli satu!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:42.23,0:22:44.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Saya juga!\N- Saya minta satu!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:44.23,0:22:45.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah. Silakan.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:46.24,0:22:48.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini akan menyelamatkan nyawaku.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:48.49,0:22:50.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Batu-batu ini sudah diberkati\Noleh Pendeta Shoko!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:50.49,0:22:52.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sekarang aku pasti selamat dari hari kiamat!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:53.74,0:22:56.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jelas-jelas ini penipuan.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:57.46,0:22:59.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tidak apa-apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:01.17,0:23:03.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tadi kau gemetaran.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:04.00,0:23:04.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yoriko.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:05.34,0:23:06.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ikut aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:06.51,0:23:08.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baik, Tuan Sogen.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:08.80,0:23:10.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu…
Dialogue: 10,0:23:10.80,0:23:12.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tuan Sogen?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:12.97,0:23:15.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukankah tadi dia ada di depan\Nbersama Pendeta Shoko?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:15.60,0:23:16.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa ini sebenarnya?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:17.14,0:23:19.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kasihan sekali si Yoriko.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:19.81,0:23:21.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kudengar ayahnya meninggal
Dialogue: 10,0:23:21.65,0:23:23.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,persis seperti ramalan Pendeta Shoko.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:24.11,0:23:26.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu akibatnya karena berani\Nmenyebut sang pendeta penipu.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:26.65,0:23:29.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia putri dari pria\Nyang kena santet sampai mati itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:32.45,0:23:33.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku harus menyelidiki kasus ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:39.29,0:23:42.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku harus menyelamatkan mereka semua.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:14.55,0:25:16.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selanjutnya, "Insiden Shorinkyo".
